title: Let's Watch TV: The Marvelous Mrs. Maisel
description:
Joe and Fran take a trip back to the late 1950's as they watch the hit Amazon Prime show The Marvelous Mrs. Maisel. Mama Fran checks Joe on his fashion knowledge and Joe gets obsessed with cult-members who have clumpy eyelashes.
